03c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: FromSoftware/Bandai Namco\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Ari Notis\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/08/Ari-Notis-Green-Purple.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=48 1x, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/08/Ari-Notis-Green-Purple.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=96 2x\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/08/Ari-Notis-Green-Purple.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=96\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/authors/ari-notis\"\u003eAri Notis\u003c/a\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(he/him) is a guides editor at Polygon, where he writes, edits, and shepherds service-oriented articles about the biggest games du jour. He previously worked at Kotaku.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/elden-ring-nightreign/514758\"\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e release time\u003c/strong\u003e is, befitting the source material, way more complicated than it needs to be.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e, a roguelike multiplayer Elden Ring game, rolls out this week with a fractured release schedule. Whether you’re playing on consoles or PC will determine when you can dive in, but even if you start at a different time than your friends, you’re not entirely missing out: As of the time of publication, \u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e does not support crossplay.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHere’s \u003cstrong\u003ewhen \u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e releases\u003c/strong\u003e depending on where you are in the world and what platform you’re playing on.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cnav\u003e\u003ch2\u003eTable of Contents\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#elden-ring-nightreign-ps5-and-xbox-release-times-1\"\u003eElden Ring Nightreign PS5 and Xbox release times\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#elden-ring-nightreign-pc-release-times\"\u003eElden Ring Nightreign PC release times\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#what-to-expect-from-elden-ring-nightreign\"\u003eWhat to expect from Elden Ring Nightreign\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/nav\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"elden-ring-nightreign-ps5-and-xbox-release-times-1\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eElden Ring Nightreign PS5 and Xbox release times\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn PlayStation and Xbox consoles, \u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e will release at \u003cstrong\u003emidnight local time on Friday, May 30\u003c/strong\u003e — with some exceptions in the Americas:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e9 p.m. PDT on May 29\u003c/strong\u003e for the west coast of North America\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e11 pm. CDT on May 29\u003c/strong\u003e for Chicago / central North America\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e1 a.m. BRT on May 30\u003c/strong\u003e for Brazil\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"elden-ring-nightreign-pc-release-times\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eElden Ring Nightreign PC release times\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1215\" data-pswp-width=\"2160\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A graphic shows the Elden Ring Nightreign release times on PC, Xbox, PS5\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/05/elden-ring-nightreign-release-times.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: FromSoftware/Bandai Namco\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn Windows PC, meanwhile, \u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e goes live at the same time around the world: \u003cstrong\u003e12 a.m. CEST on Friday, May 30\u003c/strong\u003e. Here’s when that is in your time zone:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3 p.m. PDT on May 29\u003c/strong\u003e for the west coast of North America\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e6 p.m. EDT on May 29\u003c/strong\u003e for the east coast of North America\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e11 p.m. BST on May 29\u003c/strong\u003e for the U.K.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e12 a.m. CEST\u003c/strong\u003e for western Europe/Paris\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e7 a.m. JST \u003c/strong\u003efor Japan\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e8 a.m. AEST\u003c/strong\u003e for the east coast of Australia\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"what-to-expect-from-elden-ring-nightreign\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhat to expect from Elden Ring Nightreign\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e is a multiplayer roguelike twist on Elden Ring formula, though with some unconventional matchmaking restrictions: You can play it by yourself or with \u003cem\u003etwo\u003c/em\u003e other people, but \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/news/601197/elden-ring-nightreign-2-player-duos-multiplayer\"\u003eit does not support two-player\u003c/a\u003e at launch. Sorry, duos!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor everyone else, there are eight \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/elden-ring-nightreign-guides/599387/character-classes-all-list-nightfarers\"\u003echaracter classes\u003c/a\u003e to choose from in \u003cem\u003eNightreign\u003c/em\u003e, all of which fit into predetermined character molds from the base \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e. Each run unfolds across three nights, with each night culminating in a boss fight. And some of those fights include \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/news/522765/elden-ring-nightreign-dark-souls-boss-easter-egg\"\u003ebosses from Dark Souls\u003c/a\u003e, developer FromSoftware’s notable series of action games, winking and nodding at a potential FromSoftverse.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAll told, \u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e, which sells for $40, isn’t quite as expansive as a full FromSoftware game, but more a focused spinoff for true \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e diehards. Read Polygon’s \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/gaming/522325/elden-ring-nightreign-preview-network-test\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eElden Ring Nightreign\u003c/em\u003e preview\u003c/a\u003e for more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
